{"tid":1266890,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"當自殺變成日經香港人會唔會已經冇感覺","createTime":"2019-06-29T16:14:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T16:54:09.000Z","uid":255194,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"df6fb37087492306c4ec1f1fb04722cebcfd3744","tid":1266890,"uid":255194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:14:13.000Z","msg":"雨傘失敗之後 <br />\n有幾多人對政治議題盲目左？<br />\n<br />\ndq唔關你事 <br />\n人大釋法唔關你事 <br />\n人工島？屌完兩句就冇左件事<br />\n<br />\n好多野都係香港人親手斷送係自己手上<br />\n做乜野都話冇用冇用 <br />\n有d就做完一次冇成果就放棄<br />\n有d連做都冇做就話冇用<br />\n知唔知咩叫堅持 咩叫鬥心阿<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>依家打仗阿 打贏一場仲有好多場仗要打嫁</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n日日拎住眾籌籌到幾錢 <br />\n遊行人數200萬+1個黎打飛機<br />\n士氣係緊要<br />\n但過份沉迷係呢d數字上既勝利長遠黎講係百害而無一利嫁<br />\n你要記住 自己呢一刻唔係普通市民<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地係戰士</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一個士兵唔會輕易投降<br />\n戰友戰死係唔會同個戰友講 「你咁做唔值得嫁」<br />\n而係會為戰友報仇 為戰友殺出一條血路<br />\n最後打勝仗先有面目同戰友講<br />\n「我地成功左喇」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>我地要武裝自己</strong></span><br />\n唔係裝備上咁簡單<br />\n我地仲要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">武裝自己既思想</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">悲傷</span></span>對抗爭係冇幫助<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">憎恨</span></span>先係令人更有動力既情緒<br />\n對敵人既仇恨要年年講月月講天天講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">認住 林鄭月蛾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認住 李家超 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認住 鄭若驊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認住 張建宗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認住 盧偉聰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認住 陳茂波 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認住 保皇黨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認住 班黑警 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認住 醫管局 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認住 中國共產黨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>香港人 唔好再軟弱落去<br />\n就算要死<br />\n都要攬住樓上班仆街一齊死</ins></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ee1af3a58efb3dabb1b69af95fc3b03fd5406dd0","tid":1266890,"uid":5680,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:15:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Q-kGIHSHLl0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQ-kGIHSHLl0&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=eed9c4a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Q-kGIHSHLl0</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a224cbed07dd2155b7947b63b2720137b62d6d6f","tid":1266890,"uid":255194,"like":0,"dislike":0,